1 1 New Paragraph; Fees for State Park System; Pilot Program; Community Mental Health
2 Centers. AmendRSA216-A:3-gbyinsertingafterparagraphVIIIthefollowingnewparagraph:
3 IX. The commissioner of the department of natural and cultural resources shall establish in
4 its fee package a 3-year pilot program for community mental health centers registered with the
5 department of health and human services to provide one or more passes to state parks for each
6 participating center. The commissioner shall consult with the department of health and human
7 resources to determine eligible participants, evaluation, and review of program usage. Each
8 participating community mental health center shall report annually in an anonymized data report
9 on the usage and impact of the pilot program, as well as any recommendations for changes. The
10 programshallbefundedthroughstateandfederalgrants,basedonavailablefunds,anddonations.
